    <entry>
      <title>springboot快速入门1</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/06/springboot%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A81/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/06/springboot%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A81/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一-简介"><a href="#一-简介" class="headerlink" title="一 简介"></a>一 简介</h2><ol><li>springboot入门;(掌握)</li><li>springboot入门分析;(掌握)</li><li>springboot基本使用;(掌握)</li></ol><h2 id="二-SpringBoot入门"><a href="#二-SpringBoot入门" class="headerlink" title="二.SpringBoot入门"></a>二.SpringBoot入门</h2><h3 id="1-认识SpringBoot"><a href="#1-认识SpringBoot" class="headerlink" title="1.认识SpringBoot"></a>1.认识SpringBoot</h3><h4 id="1-1-什么是SpringBoot"><a href="#1-1-什么是SpringBoot" class="headerlink" title="1.1.什么是SpringBoot"></a>1.1.什么是SpringBoot</h4><blockquote><p>Spring Boot是其设计目的是用来<strong>简化Spring应用（用到spring开发的项目）的初始搭建以及开发过程</strong>。该框架使用了特定的方式来进行配置，从而使开发人员不再需要定义样板化的配置。</p></blockquote><h4 id="1-2-SpringBoot的特点"><a href="#1-2-SpringBoot的特点" class="headerlink" title="1.2.SpringBoot的特点"></a>1.2.SpringBoot的特点</h4><p>​SpringBoot是一个框架，可以非常快速的开发spring应用，SpringBoot具有如下特点：</p><ul><li>简化Maven，管理了大量的基础依赖</li><li>基于注解配置(JavaConfig)&#x2F;无需xml，自动装配功能,简化大量配置</li><li>内嵌tomcat,部署简单</li><li>更加方便的和三方框架集成-mybatis等</li><li>健康检查，支持外部化配置等</li></ul><p>idea中maven多模块：</p><p> <strong>springboot-parent:项目 ,只是用来管理子模块，里面不会写代码</strong></p><p>​        <strong>springboot-01-hello：模块，普通maven，java</strong></p><p>​        springboot-02–config：模块，普通maven，java</p><p>​       springboot-03–web：模块，普通maven，java</p><p>​        springboot-04–mybatis：模块，普通maven，java</p><p>​       springboot-05–tx：模块，普通maven，java</p><p><img src="/2023/10/06/springboot%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A81/1658369462302.png" alt="1658369462302"></p><p><img src="/2023/10/06/springboot%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A81/1658369477456.png" alt="1658369477456"></p><h3 id="2-HelloWorld程序【重要】"><a href="#2-HelloWorld程序【重要】" class="headerlink" title="2.HelloWorld程序【重要】"></a>2.HelloWorld程序【重要】</h3><p>​这里我们来做一个简单的web程序，大家可以回顾一下使用SpirngMVC如何实现一个web应用，然后对比SpringBoot实现web应用，看一下有什么区别</p><h4 id="2-1-导入依赖"><a href="#2-1-导入依赖" class="headerlink" title="2.1.导入依赖"></a>2.1.导入依赖</h4><p>spring-boot-starter-parent是SpringBoot的父工程，通过继承的方式引入，spring-boot-starter-web是SpringBoot集成web的依赖，主要包括了SpingMVC,Tomcat,日志,自动配置等等相关依赖</p><ul><li>springboot-parent</li></ul><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">parent</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-parent<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span>2.0.5.RELEASE<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">parent</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>springboot-01-hello</li></ul><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-web<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2023/10/06/springboot%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A81/1658370003764.png" alt="1658370003764"></p><h4 id="2-2-创建启动类"><a href="#2-2-创建启动类" class="headerlink" title="2.2.创建启动类"></a>2.2.创建启动类</h4><p>@SpringBootApplication注解是SpringBoot的主启动注解，贴在主启动类上， <strong>SpringApplication.run的作用是启动内置的Tomcat</strong>，运行SpringBoot的应用。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@SpringBootApplication</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ApplicationConfig</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        SpringApplication.run(ApplicationConfig.class);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-3-配置文件application-properties"><a href="#2-3-配置文件application-properties" class="headerlink" title="2.3 配置文件application.properties"></a>2.3 配置文件application.properties</h4><figure class="highlight properties"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">server.port</span>=<span class="string">80</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-4-编写Controller"><a href="#2-4-编写Controller" class="headerlink" title="2.4.编写Controller"></a>2.4.编写Controller</h4><p>编写一个简单的controller进行测试，@RestController注解是@Controller和@ResponseBody的组合注解</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@RestController</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Example</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@RequestMapping(&quot;/hello&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line">String <span class="title function_">home</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;Hello World!&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-5-启动测试"><a href="#2-5-启动测试" class="headerlink" title="2.5.启动测试"></a>2.5.启动测试</h4><p>执行main方法启动，浏览器访问：<a href="http://localhost:8080/hello">http://localhost:8080/hello</a></p><h2 id="三-SpringBoot分析【重要】"><a href="#三-SpringBoot分析【重要】" class="headerlink" title="三.SpringBoot分析【重要】"></a>三.SpringBoot分析【重要】</h2><p>通过上面的HellWorld程序我们确实感知到SpringBoot的方便之处，如此快速的就能开发一个Web应用这是以前不可想象的，但是在这些快捷开发的背后不免有些问题，比如：为什么要继承spring-boot-starter-parent，它的作用是什么？spring-boot-starter-web又干了啥？下面我们就来了解一下这些让我们疑惑的地方。</p><h3 id="1-spring-boot-starter-parent"><a href="#1-spring-boot-starter-parent" class="headerlink" title="1.spring-boot-starter-parent"></a>1.spring-boot-starter-parent</h3><p>在pom.xml中我们通过<parent> 继承了 <code>spring-boot-starter-parent</code>，我们说这个项目是SpringBoot的父工程</parent></p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">parent</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-parent<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span>2.0.5.RELEASE<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">parent</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>上面有介绍到，这个项目是SpringBoot的父工程，它的作用是帮我们管理了很多的基础jar包，有兴趣的小伙伴可以按住ctrl点进去看一下，在spring-boot-starter-parent中其实还继承了spring-boot-dependencies，在spring-boot-dependencies项目中通过<dependencyManagement>管理了非常多的依赖，同时通过&lt;<properties>维护了这些依赖的version ，总结一下就是SpringBoot的父工程帮我们管理了很多的基础依赖。</properties></dependencyManagement></p><p>当我们继承了<code>spring-boot-starter-parent</code>就意味着我们成为了SpringBoot的一个子项目，拥有使用SpringBoot中管理的依赖的权利，但是还不能直接使用，需要在自己的项目中通过通过<dependencies> 去导入具体的依赖才行，当然version我们可以不用指定了，因为父项目已经维护了verion,除非你要自己指定自己的version。</dependencies></p><p>这里普及一下pom.xml中的 <dependencyManagement>和 <dependencies> 的区别</dependencies></dependencyManagement></p><ul><li>dependencyManagement ：是用来管理或者说是声明依赖，其中的依赖并不能直接使用，需要在dependencies中显示的导入才可以用</li><li>dependencies：是用来导入依赖，其中的依赖可以直接使用</li></ul><h3 id="2-spring-boot-starter-web"><a href="#2-spring-boot-starter-web" class="headerlink" title="2.spring-boot-starter-web"></a>2.spring-boot-starter-web</h3><p>spring-boot-starter-web这个项目是SpringBoot和SpringMvc整合的jar包，并且导入了日志，tomcat,等等相关的jar包</p><p><img src="/2023/10/06/springboot%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A81/1618364844612-1618372707261.png" alt="1618364844612"></p><h3 id="3-SpringBootApplication"><a href="#3-SpringBootApplication" class="headerlink" title="3.@SpringBootApplication"></a>3.@SpringBootApplication</h3><p>这个注解是SpringBoot的一个组合注解，一般用来贴在主启动类用，它主要包括三个标签组成</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@SpringBootConfiguration</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@EnableAutoConfiguration</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@ComponentScan(excludeFilters = &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Filter(type = FilterType.CUSTOM, classes = TypeExcludeFilter.class),</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Filter(type = FilterType.CUSTOM, classes = AutoConfigurationExcludeFilter.class) &#125;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="meta">@interface</span> SpringBootApplication &#123;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里解释一下@SpringBootApplication上面的三个注解</p><ul><li><p>@SpringBootConfiguration: 这个注解是SpringBoot的配置注解其本质是一个@Configuration即Spring的配置注解，或者说如果一个类贴了@Configuration注解或@SpringBootConfiguration或@SpringBootApplication的类都可以被识别成Spring的配置类</p></li><li><p>@ComponentScan : 这个注解是Spring的IOC自动扫描注解，作用类似于<code>&lt;context:componentScan /&gt;</code>，该注解默认可以扫描当前主启动类所在包及其子包中的有注解了@Controller,@Service,@Repository,@Component,@Configuration 的类，自动注册到Spring容器中。</p></li><li><p>1.4.@EnableAutoConfiguration : 这个注解是开启SpringBoot自动配置的注解，它是SpringBoot可以快速开发，简化配置的主要原因。</p></li></ul><h3 id="4-SpringApplication-run"><a href="#4-SpringApplication-run" class="headerlink" title="4.SpringApplication.run"></a>4.SpringApplication.run</h3><p>它的作用是启动SpringBoot项目，底层会创建IOC容器，进行Bean的初始化，也会走自动配置流程，最后会运行内置Tomcat启动项目</p><h2 id="四-SpringBoot基本使用"><a href="#四-SpringBoot基本使用" class="headerlink" title="四.SpringBoot基本使用"></a>四.SpringBoot基本使用</h2><h3 id="1-SpringBoot基础功能"><a href="#1-SpringBoot基础功能" class="headerlink" title="1.SpringBoot基础功能"></a>1.SpringBoot基础功能</h3><h4 id="1-1-项目结构"><a href="#1-1-项目结构" class="headerlink" title="1.1.项目结构"></a>1.1.项目结构</h4><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src</span><br><span class="line">--main</span><br><span class="line">--java</span><br><span class="line">--resources</span><br><span class="line">--static//静态资源目录 img,js,css</span><br><span class="line">--templates//模板页面目录，如：jsp ,ftl</span><br><span class="line">--application.properties/application.yml//默认配置文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>java ：java目录是代码所在目录</p></li><li><p>resources&#x2F;static :静态资源目，springBoot默认的静态资源路径有五个，按照优先级分别是项目的根路径 &#x2F;，classpath:&#x2F;META-INF&#x2F;resources&#x2F;，classpath:&#x2F;resources&#x2F;，classpath:&#x2F;static&#x2F;，classpath:&#x2F;public&#x2F;</p></li><li><p>resources&#x2F;templates :模板文件所在目录，比如 .jsp,.ftl等等</p></li><li><p>resources&#x2F;application.properties,application.yml  : SpringBoot默认配置文件</p></li></ul><h4 id="1-2-独立运行"><a href="#1-2-独立运行" class="headerlink" title="1.2.独立运行"></a>1.2.独立运行</h4><ul><li>1.导入打包插件</li></ul><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">build</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">plugins</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-maven-plugin<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">plugins</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">build</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>2.执行打包命令，使用终端进入项目根目录执行 <code>mvn package</code> ，或者点击：</li></ul><p> <img src="/2023/10/06/springboot%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A81/1568515028409.png" alt="1568515028409"></p><ul><li>3.打包命令会把jar打包到<code>target</code>目录，进入该目录，启动项目，运行</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java -jar xxx.jar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以通过 –添加指定配置，比如：<code>java -jar xxx.jar -–server.port=8888</code></p><h4 id="1-3-热部署"><a href="#1-3-热部署" class="headerlink" title="1.3.热部署"></a>1.3.热部署</h4><p>SpringBoot提供了热部署解决方案spring-boot-devtools，它是通过检测classpath中的字节码变化重新编译项目的方式来实现热部署，个人建议程序员不要太过依赖热部署功能(你是否也踩过坑)</p><ul><li>1.导入依赖</li></ul><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-devtools<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>2.编译代码</li></ul><blockquote><p>ctrl + F9</p></blockquote><ul><li>访问测试</li></ul><h4 id="1-4-yml基本语法"><a href="#1-4-yml基本语法" class="headerlink" title="1.4.yml基本语法"></a>1.4.yml基本语法</h4><p>在SpringBoot中可以使用application.properties 或者 application.yml(yaml) 或者bootstrap.yml(yaml) 作为默认的配置文件，bootstrap.yml的优先级最高，通常用来整合配置中心使用。 yml是一种全新的语言，他有自己的格式，比如在properties中配置的  server.port&#x3D;8888  在yml中配置体现为：</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">server:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">port:</span> <span class="number">8888</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里做一个简单的格式说明：</p><ul><li><p>k:(空格)v：表示一对键值对（空格必须有）；</p></li><li><p>以空格的缩进来控制层级关系；只要是左对齐的一列数据，都是同一个层级的</p></li><li><p>多个级之间用冒号 : 来分类，并且换行缩进 ， 如果是值就不用换行，值前面有个空格</p></li><li><p>属性和值也是大小写敏感；</p></li></ul><p>举例：配置一个User对象在properties中的配置如：</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">user.username</span>=zs</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">user.password</span>=<span class="number">123</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在yml中的配置如：</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">user:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">username:</span> <span class="string">zs</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">password:</span> <span class="number">123</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者使用行内写法：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">user:</span> &#123;<span class="attr">username:</span> <span class="string">zs</span>,<span class="attr">password:</span> <span class="number">123</span>&#125;  <span class="comment">#不推荐</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>yml中值的写法：</p><ul><li>字面量：普通的值（数字，字符串，布尔） ， k: v：字面直接来写；字符串默认不用加上单引号或者双引号；</li><li>“”：双引号；不会转义字符串里面的特殊字符；特殊字符会作为本身想表示的意思 name:   “zhangsan \n lisi”：输出；zhangsan 换行  lisi</li><li>‘’：单引号；会转义特殊字符，特殊字符最终只是一个普通的字符串数据 name:   ‘zhangsan \n lisi’：输出；zhangsan \n  lisi</li></ul><p>k: v：在下一行来写对象的属性和值的关系；注意缩进 ， 对象还是k: v的方式</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">friends:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">lastName:</span> <span class="string">zhangsan</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">age:</span> <span class="number">20</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>数组（List、Set）,用- 值表示数组中的一个元素</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">pets:</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">cat</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">dog</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">pig</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者写成：pets: [cat,dog,pig]</p><h4 id="1-5-SpringBoot读取配置【重要】"><a href="#1-5-SpringBoot读取配置【重要】" class="headerlink" title="1.5.SpringBoot读取配置【重要】"></a>1.5.SpringBoot读取配置【重要】</h4><ul><li>方式一：使用@Value 配置文件</li></ul><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">user:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  username:</span> ls</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  password:</span> <span class="number">456</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  age:</span> <span class="number">99</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用@Value标签读取配置</p><figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">User</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//@Value :从配置文件中取值   SPEL</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Value(<span class="string">&quot;<span class="subst">$&#123;user.username&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String username = <span class="string">&quot;zs&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Value(<span class="string">&quot;<span class="subst">$&#123;user.password&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String password = <span class="string">&quot;123&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Value(<span class="string">&quot;<span class="subst">$&#123;user.age&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> int age = <span class="number">18</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    . . . . . . </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>方式二：使用@ConfigurationProperties， 配置文件</li></ul><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">employee:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">username:</span> <span class="string">ls</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">password:</span> <span class="number">456</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">age:</span> <span class="number">99</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>绑定配置的对象</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@ConfigurationProperties(prefix = &quot;employee&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Employee</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">username</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;zs&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">password</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;123&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">age</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">18</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>@ConfigurationProperties : 自动的根据前缀从配置中过滤出配置项目，然后根据当前对象的列名进行匹配，自动赋值。</p><h4 id="1-6-多环境配置切换【重要】"><a href="#1-6-多环境配置切换【重要】" class="headerlink" title="1.6.多环境配置切换【重要】"></a>1.6.多环境配置切换【重要】</h4><p>一套代码需要部署到不同环境，一套代码不同配置就OK</p><p><img src="/2023/10/06/springboot%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A81/1658389887829.png" alt="1658389887829"></p><ul><li>方式一：使用单个配置文件实现多环境配置</li></ul><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">spring:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">profiles:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">active:</span> <span class="string">dev</span><span class="comment">#激活(选择)环境test</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">spring:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">profiles:</span> <span class="string">dev</span><span class="comment">#指定环境名字dev</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">server:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">port:</span> <span class="number">9999</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">spring:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">profiles:</span> <span class="string">test</span><span class="comment">#指定环境名字test</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">server:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">port:</span> <span class="number">8888</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>方式二：使用多配置文件，通过配置文件的名字来识别环境</li></ul><p>application-dev.yml</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">server:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">port:</span> <span class="number">9999</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>application-test.yml</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">server:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">port:</span> <span class="number">8888</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>application.yml</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">spring:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">profiles:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">active:</span> <span class="string">test</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#根据文件名字配置 application-dev.properties</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过修改运行的参数，指定运行环境：</p><p>-Dspring.profiles.active&#x3D;dev</p><p>部署时采用命令指定运行环境：</p><p>java -jar xx-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar –spring.profiles.active&#x3D;dev</p><h4 id="1-7-SpringBoot读取-properties和xml"><a href="#1-7-SpringBoot读取-properties和xml" class="headerlink" title="1.7.SpringBoot读取 properties和xml"></a>1.7.SpringBoot读取 properties和xml</h4><p>SpringBoot默认加载application.yml ,application.properties作为配置文件，也可以使用下面的注解加载额外的配置文件</p><ul><li>@PropertySource(“classpath:aa.properties”) ：加载一个properties配置文件</li><li><strong>@ImportResource(“classpath:application-context.xml”):加载一个xml配置文件</strong></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
